OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The US has approved the first pill for 
OL,6, postpartum depression.                 
OL,8,FThe Food and Drug Administration (FDA) 
OL,9,Fsaid zuranolone, sold under the brand  
OL,10,Fname Zurzuvae, has been approved as a  
OL,11,Fonce-daily pill taken for two weeks.   
OL,13,FUntil now, treatment for postpartum    
OL,14,Fdepression (PPD) was available only as 
OL,15,Fan intravenous injection, the FDA said.
OL,17,FDrug manufacturers Sage Therapeutics   
OL,18,Fand Biogen said the pill is expected to
OL,19,Fbe available later this year. No price 
OL,20,Fhas yet been announced.                
